---
title: Tuscan-Style Cannellini Beans with Zucchini and Tomato Spring Greens
description: Mediterranean spices elevate the flavour of these simple beans. Paired perfectly with roasted potatoes and a fresh spring salad for a hearty veggie dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/haricots-cannellini-a-la-toscane-8f02e25e.jpg
